### Time complexity

Each additional line roughly doubles the time taken to reject the input.

### Where it's slow

From `-Z time-passes`:

* the slow pass is `parse_crate`

From [sample-head.txt](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/files/10138299/sample-head.txt): 

* [`annotate_following_item_if_applicable`](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/1eb62b1235fd77200e6bd967d70e83c0f2497233/compiler/rustc_parse/src/parser/attr.rs#L138) is on the stack repeatedly

### Regression

Regression in nightly-2021-09-06, likely from #88257 (@estebank)

